item.title: Dell AT102W
item.description: History Dell AT102W is one of the mass-produced Alps Bigfoot series keyboards made in the late 90s. Dell used to ship them with their personal computers. The early Dell keyboards, such as Dell AT 101 were made by Alps Electric, but the later models like this one were made by Silitek. Dell AT102W back side Build and Features Dell AT102W with SKCM Blacks The board has Alps SKCM Black switches, which are in pristine condition.
